# Real-Time Industrial IoT Monitoring System

This project implements a hybrid edge-cloud monitoring solution using Raspberry Pi, Azure IoT Hub, Power BI, and more.

## Tools Used
- Python, MQTT, Node-RED, InfluxDB, Azure IoT Hub, Power BI

## Key Features
- <50ms latency local visualization
- Real-time fault detection
- Scalable to 10,000+ data points/min
